ArchiTect command list

CommandDescription
/greetGreet a user of your choice
/helpShows you a list with all the commands
/kickKick a member of your choice
/saySay something as the bot
/userinfoDisplays every information about the selected user
/clearClear messages in the channel
/embedCreate an embed for you
/csgo_mapsDisplays your selected CS:GO map
/memberlistShows you a list of the members on the server
/banBan a user of your choice
/radio playJoin a voice channel, select a radio station, and enjoy one of 5 integrated radio stations
/stopStop the current music
/leaveLeave the voice channel
/serverinfoGet all the useful information about the server you are on
/timeoutSend a user to a timeout
/unmuteUnmute a member after a timeout
/nick setChange the nickname of a user
/nick defaultReset the current nickname to the default
/create passwordCreates you a very strong password with a huge impact of characters
/give messagesRead the channel history and show you the value of the sent messages
/rankGet your registered rank
/pingGet the bot's ping/latency
/botShows you useful information about the bot
/rolesShows you all the roles on the server
/automod filter_invitesFilter every single invite link sent to your selected channel
/automod filter_insultFilter every single insult sent to your selected channel
